field.value:
When saveFiles="true" and temporarySourceFilesDirectory is set in the config, vcompile will fail with an FileNotFoundException. This is caused by the fact that the file names of the generated files are passed to the csharp compiler without the directory.

A solution is attached in the patch. 

AbstractCompiler.cs:
protected string SourceFileToFileName(SourceFile file)
{
	// was: return file.FileName;
	return Path.Combine(context.TemporarySourceFilesDirectory.FullName, file.FileName);
}
